# Real snapshot archives contain hostnames, usernames, IP addresses,
# listening services, firewall topology, and operational baseline.
# Never commit real snapshots to a public or shared repository.
security-snapshot-*/
security-snapshot-*.tar.gz
kunadonokami-snapshot-*/
kunadonokami-snapshot-*.tar.gz

# Local policy overrides should not be committed to the public repository.
*.local
*.tmp

# Editor and OS noise.
.DS_Store
*~

# Coding agents
AGENTS.md
